I recall using 2" dia. exhaust hose from West Marine.  This hose is
used for 'wet exhaust' out the transom of a boat.  Sold by the foot.
The hose was so tough that I had to use a hacksaw to cut it and
wire cutters for the embedded wire.  It's still working after 9 years.

